summary:
Business Intelligence Manager with experience delivering professional analytical systems and analysing complex data and processes across a variety of industries (manufacturing, retail and banking). Able to interpret systems, remap operational processes to deliver efficiencies, and work across various internal departments to help deliver excellent customer service and products. Fluent in Russian and English. 

Please contact me via LinkedIn or at alisa2066@gmail.com
